{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"accumulate","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/accumulate","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>« <a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Attribute\" title=\"en/SVG/Attribute\">SVG 属性参考主页</a></p>\n\n<p>该属性控制了动画是否是累加的。</p>\n\n<p>在原来的结果的基础上重复动画的时候，它通常很有用，每一次循环都累加。这个属性告诉动画是否是每次循环，前一个动画属性值要加上去。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"用法","title":"用法","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">类别</th>\n   <td>动画累加属性</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">值</th>\n   <td><strong>none</strong> | sum</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">可变性</th>\n   <td>No</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">规范文档</th>\n   <td><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG/animate.html#AdditionAttributes\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition)</a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"sum\">sum</dt>\n <dd>指定第一次循环后的每次循环建立在上次循环的终值上。</dd>\n <dt id=\"none\">none</dt>\n <dd>指定重复循环是不累加的。这是默认值。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"元素","title":"元素","isH3":false,"content":"<p>以下元素可以使用<code>additive</code>属性：</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/animate\"><code>&lt;animate&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/animate\"><code>&lt;animateColor&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/animateMotion\"><code>&lt;animateMotion&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/animateTransform\"><code>&lt;animateTransform&gt;</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"用法","id":"用法"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"元素","id":"元素"}],"summary":"« SVG 属性参考主页","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"accumulate","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/accumulate","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/accumulate/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG","title":"SVG"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute","title":"SVG 属性参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/accumulate","title":"accumulate"}],"pageTitle":"accumulate - SVG | MDN","noIndexing":false}}